title: Manicure
about: The Nail Lounge of La Jolla offers a variety of manicures to suit your needs. Whether you seek a simple shine or a complete pampering, there is a perfect manicure for you.

title: Pedicure
about: The Nail Lounge of La Jolla has a variety of spa pedicures. Whether you would like simple renewal and refreshment, or an all-out pampering session, The Nail Lounge of La Jolla has what you’re looking for.

title: Nail Enhancement
about: Nail enhancements are perfect for those who wish to optimize their natural nail by enhancing it with a variety of nail enhancement techniques. Great for an every day look or a special occasion, nail enhancements make the most of your nails.

title: Waxing
about: The Nail Lounge of La Jolla offers waxing for anybody’s needs. Waxing leaves skin soft and renewed, giving you confidence to show beautiful skin.

title: Kids Service
about: Little Princess treatments are for our guests age ten and younger. Perfect as gifts or to accompany your own spa experience, Little Princess treatments will make her feel extra special.

title: Additional Services
about: The Nail Lounge of La Jolla offers additional services to ensure your satisfaction. Anything from changing your nail polish color to repairing a broken nail to having a few extra minutes of massage can be done for you.
